    Process called "create_scipy_interface" returns ScipyCompat:
    Return ScipyCompat with:
    stats as create_scipy_stats()
    optimize as create_scipy_optimize()
    integrate as create_scipy_integrate()
    interpolate as create_scipy_interpolate()
    signal as create_scipy_signal()
