Process called "pearsonr_wrapper" that takes args as List[Any] returns Any:
    Let x be args at index 0
    Let y be args at index 1
    Return StatsCore.pearson_correlation with x as x and y as y

Process called "spearmanr_wrapper" that takes args as List[Any] returns Any:
